            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Ok this makes perfect sense, I think that with my approach the attacker would need a number of clients proportional to the size of the group, but it does not make the attack unfeasable in any way.\r\nThis said, I understand how the new implementation would be the best solution, and I don't see any reason to push this issue further until maybe we see heavy performance issues with the new implementation.",
